    "description": "<p>While wearing this helm, you gain the following benefits: </p><p>• You can use an action to cast detect thoughts (save DC 13) at will. While maintaining concentration, you can use a bonus action to send a telepathic message to a creature you are focused on. It can reply with a bonus action while you are focused on it. If a creature successfully saves against this property, it becomes immune to it for 24 hours. </p><p>• Once between long rests, while focusing on a creature with detect thoughts you can use an action to cast suggestion (save DC 13) on that creature.</p>",
